":"2019-07-01T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"仲幫班賤種洗白<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會再犯5年前嘅錯   你要走舊路你嘅事   <br />\n<br />\n咪撚上黎連登講  自己寫日記  唔該曬"},{"pid":"ccd8eced82e64a57c795fe9192d488f655368661","tid":1274921,"uid":183348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:56:38.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"d7240af881bda33a7a02f6cb5adb8fb2f3d433f8","tid":1274921,"uid":22715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be84446bd8828c8f6188c88d983f66fc4d492ae6","tid":1274921,"uid":179409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:01:45.000Z","msg":"成個警隊高層一早染紅晒<br />\n佢哋係幫中共對付緊香港人<br />\n而下面班細只會盲目聽從上頭命令<br />\n你點感動到佢哋？<br />\n依家係成個警隊本身定位<br />\n都唔係效忠香港人<br />\n而係效忠共產黨<br />\n係成個警隊結構問題<br />\n唔關警察有無良心事"},{"pid":"70fc868a0bd718714871fc9d5beb748e87ea973c","tid":1274921,"uid":18962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:02:35.000Z","msg":"班廢物賣屎忽都搵唔返而家份糧 慳返啖氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}